replies.body:
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-popcorn}} 
It looks like you may have encountered a new [**phishing attempt**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204230720-Phishing-Don-t-take-the-bait) that hackers have developed. The email you received was not from Riot Games, but was sent by someone trying to get access to your account. 

I'd _**highly**_ suggest reaching out to us through our [**account recovery form**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416) in order to help secure your account. Also, keep in mind that we will only try to help you recover you account through these tickets, and will never reach out to you on our own asking for personal information.
